	<h1 class="title">圣诞还早，英国最酷百货公司已经布置好了橱窗</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">魏云峰</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-03 08:23:10 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3193/medium/3193.jpg?1436637072" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="3193" data-title="《圣诞还早，英国最酷百货公司已经布置好了橱窗》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3193/medium/3193.jpg?1436637072" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3193.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
